snippet.title: Rapid roll Gameplay/First look. (Nokia 105)
snippet.description:
Today we take a look at the pre installed game called Rapid roll in the Nokia 105. 
All music used is royalty free.
LIKE AND SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE GAMEPLAY VIDEOS. I will be doing commentary as soon as i move out of my parents house.
